00:11:27.639 --> 00:11:28.559
Chị mau ăn đi.

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.000
Canh sắp nguội rồi.

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:09.200
Chị.

00:12:16.639 --> 00:12:17.120
Chị ơi.

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:17.960
